Section : Model scheduling (100) Attachment :
Workloading : (Min) LeadingTime : (Min) Phase :

Note: for versions before 1.3.3 please perform steps 1-9 ,From 1.3.3 version and later please execute steps 10-17.
Notes：Please cover AC and DC mode, AC and DC are expected to be the same
1. Open Lenovo AI Now
Ensure AI Now enter High performance mode. High performance mode:The model service is fully loaded in task manager(processes)

2. Idle about 5 mins

Ensure AI Now enter energy saving mode. Energy saving mode: The model frees up some resources, but the process is there in task manager
3. Exit Lenovo AI Now
Ensure there is no model service and pfm service in Task Manager
4. Open Lenovo AI Now
Ensure AI Now enter High performance mode. High performance mode:The model service is fully loaded in task manager
5. Click "x" and AI Now will enter the tray
Ensure AI Now enter energy saving mode. Energy saving mode: The model frees up some resources, but the process is there in task manager

6. Idle about 5 mins

Ensure AI Now enter idle mode. Idle mode: there is no model service and pfm service in Task Manager
7. Press ctrl+Q/Right-click the AI Now tray icon to open Mini Lenovo AI Now
Ensure AI Now enter High performance mode. High performance mode:The model service is fully loaded in task manager

8. Idle about 2 mins

The Mini AI Now UI will disappear and ensure AI Now enter energy saving mode. Energy saving mode: The model frees up some resources, but the process is there in task manager

9. Idle about 5 mins

Ensure AI Now enter idle mode. Idle mode: there is no model service and pfm service in Task Manager

Notes：Please cover AC and DC mode, AC and DC are expected to be the same

10. Open Lenovo AI Now

Ensure AI Now enter High performance mode. High performance mode:The "model service" and "pfmservice" is fully loaded in task manager(processes)

11. Idle about 5 mins

Ensure AI Now enter Cache mode. Cache mode: The "model service" process has disappeared, "pfmservice" exists but consumes fewer resources.

12. Exit Lenovo AI Now

Ensure there is no model service and pfmservice in Task Manager

13. Open Lenovo AI Now

Ensure AI Now enter High performance mode. High performance mode:The "model service" and "pfmservice" is fully loaded in task manager

14. Click "x" and AI Now will enter the tray

Ensure AI Now enter Cache mode. Cache mode: The "model service" process has disappeared, "pfmservice" exists but consumes fewer resources

15.  1.3.3 version：Press ctrl+Q/Right-click the AI Now tray icon to open Mini Lenovo AI Now

Ensure AI Now enter High performance mode. High performance mode:The "model service" and "pfmservice" is fully loaded in task manager

16. 1.4.0version and later:Press ctrl+Q/Right-click the AI Now tray icon to open Search Bar. In the dialog box, enter 'How is China's economic development' then select 'Ask AINOW'（Notes: You need to add related problem files to the knowledge base so the AI Now will answer.）

Ensure AI Now enter High performance mode. High performance mode:The "model service" and "pfmservice" is fully loaded in task manager

17. Idle about 2 mins

The Mini Lenovo AI Now(1.3.3)/Search Bar(1.4.0 and later) UI will disappear and ensure AI Now enter Cache mode. Cache mode: The "model service" process has disappeared, "pfmservice" exists but consumes fewer resources
 
Section : Meeting Assistant (120) Attachment :
Workloading : (Min) LeadingTime : (Min) Phase :
Excute below test case, please ensure LSM version is 2.7.15 and later. If Lenovo Smart Meeting is not pre-installed, skip 1.1 to 3.4
1. Smart Fusion
Note: Connect a Webcam camera which support dual camera fusion function
1.1 Initiate a meeting by using teams and choose "Lenovo virtual camera"
1.2 Open Lenovo AI Now, enter below content in dialog box and click send button (EN:Turn on dual camera fusion)
Lenovo AI Now will call up dual camera fusion function of LSM.
1.3 Enable all functions in build-in camera settings and magic webcam settings
Ensure all functions works normal and can be closed normally
2. Temporary Departure
2.1 Initiate a meeting by using teams and choose "Lenovo virtual camera"
2.2 Open Lenovo AI Now, enter below content in dialog box and click send button (EN: leave a while)
Lenovo AI Now will call up temp avatar function of LSM
2.3 Start counting down three seconds
Ensure the record can generate successfully
2.4 Leave the meeting and check the video
Ensure temp avatar function take effect by Lenovo AI Now setting
2.5 Click "Back Now" button in Lenovo Lenovo AI Now window
Ensuer temp avatar function close successfully
3. Call-up AI Meeting Minutes(Current version not support AI Meeting munities, please skip below steps)
3.1 Initiate a meeting by using teams
3.2 Open Lenovo AI Now, enter below content in dialog box and click send button (EN: Start AI meeting munites)
Lenovo AI Now opens conference transliteration and gets to work normally.
3.3 Click "Stop AI meeting munites".
Lenovo AI Now stop conference transliteration and create AI digest.
3.4 Enter "Exit AI meeting munites" on the home page and send it.
Conference transliteration can be turned off.

Section : Compatibility Test (120) Attachment :
Workloading : (Min) LeadingTime : (Min) Phase :
1 Modify power mode to default mode
Ensure power mode can modify successfully
2 Download and install below 3rd party applications: Chrome, Teams, MSFT PPT
3 Press Smartkey to launch Lenovo AI Now application (Web release AI Now does not support Smartkey)
Ensure Lenovo AI Now can launch without error
4 Launch Edge and open 5 webpages, do some browsing actions
Ensure Edge webpage can launch and browsing without lag
5 Launch Teams and start a teams call (Note: Edge in background)
Ensure Teams call can play without lag
6 Stop teams call and minimized the window, lauch MSFT PPT and instart some pictures
Ensure MSFT PPT can work without lag
7 In Lenovo AI Now window, select the file " China's economic development I " to summary in Lenovo AI Now interface. Notes: You need to add related problem files to the knowledge base.
Ensure the summary generate successfully without error
8 Press Alt+Tab button to switch all applications for 10 times
Ensure the application can switch successfully without lag
DC RSOC<20% repeat step 1-8
Ensure without lag or error

System can enter into MS/S3 without error.
3.Resume from MS/S3, select the file " China's economic development III " to summary in Lenovo AI Now interface.
Ensure the summary generate successfully without error
4. Repeat step 2-3 5 times
Lenovo AI Now works normally.
5.Put system into S4 and wait for 1 min
System can enter into S4 without error.
6.Resume from S4 , select the file " China's economic development IV " to summary in Lenovo AI Now interface.
Ensure the summary generate successfully without error
7. Repeat step 5-6 5 times
Lenovo AI Now works normally.
8.Put system to WB.
System can enter into WB without error.
9.When WB complete, launch AI Now in All apps/smartkey and select the file " China's economic development V " to summary. (Notes: Web release AI Now does not support Smartkey)
Ensure the summary generate successfully without error
10. Repeat step 8-9 5 times
Lenovo AI Now works normally.
11.Put system to CB
System can enter into CB without error.
12.Press power button and enter to system, launch AI Now in All apps/smartkey (Notes: Web release AI Now does not support Smartkey)
Lenovo AI Now can launch successfully
13.Select the file " Node " to summary in Lenovo AI Now interface.
Ensure the summary generate successfully without error
14. Repeat step 11-13 5 times
Lenovo AI Now works normally.

16. Select the file " Node " to summary in Lenovo AI Now interface.
Ensure the summary generate successfully without error
17. Click x to close Lenovo AI Now and idle for 10 mins
Ensure Lenovo AI Now list in system tray in lower right corner

Section : Modify GPU working mode Test (120) Attachment :
Workloading : (Min) LeadingTime : (Min) Phase :
Notes:Test steps 1.1-1.6 require changing this feature in vantage,If not support, skip it
1.1 Modify GPU workingr mode to iGPU only mode in vantage
Make sure the machine is in iGPU only mode
1.2 Open the AI Now check main function
Ensure that the main function of the AI Now is normal（Notes：If the cpu name suffix is H/HX or igpu is Intel® UHD Graphics or memory size is less than 16 GB, it is normal for the AI Now to pop up an Hardware detection)
1.3 Exit AI Now, and modify GPU workingr mode to Hybrid Mode in vantage
Make sure the machine is in Hybrid Mode
1.4 Open the AI Now check main function
Ensure that the main function of the AI Now is normal
1.5 Modify GPU workingr mode to Discrete Graphics in BIOS
Make sure the machine is in dGPU only mode
1.6 Open the AI Now check main function(Switch back to the default mode after testing)
Ensure that the main function of the AI Now is normal
Notes:Test steps 2.1-2.6 require changing this feature in Legion space,If not support, skip it
2.1 Modify GPU workingr mode to Hybrid-Igpu Only Mode in Legion space
Make sure the machine is in Hybrid-Igpu Only Mode
2.2 Open the AI Now check main function
Ensure that the main function of the AI Now is normal（Notes：If the cpu name suffix is H/HX or igpu is Intel® UHD Graphics or memory size is less than 16 GB, it is normal for the AI Now to pop up an Hardware detection)
2.3 Exit AI Now, and modify GPU workingr mode to Hybrid Mode in Legion space
Make sure the machine is in Hybrid Mode
2.4 Open the AI Now check main function
Ensure that the main function of the AI Now is normal
2.5 Exit AI Now, and modify GPU workingr mode to dGPU Mode in Legion space
Make sure the machine is in dGPU Mode(Notes:The machine may need to be restarted)
2.6 Open the AI Now check main function(Switch back to the default mode after testing)
Ensure that the main function of the AI Now is normal
